Omuwendo gw'abantu abalina obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19) gukwatagana mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK, ekiraga nti wadde nga embeera zaawukana okusinziira ku mawanga, COVID-19 eyongedde okwonooneka mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku kyokulabirako kya Italy, amawanga, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'okulabiriramu abalwadde ab'amaanyi (ICU) birina okwongera okwetegekera omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abajja okwetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala ICU.
Nga 31 December 2019, waliwo ekibinja ky'abalwadde ba pulomyeeya ab'ensonga etamanyiddwa mu kibuga Wuhan, mu ssaza lya Hubei, mu China.
Nga 9 January 2020, ekitongole kya China eky'okufuga n'okutangira endwadde kyagamba nti ekirwadde ekireetawo akawuka ka Corona kati kayitibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva ku SARS-CoV-2 buyitibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obuliwo bukakasa nti abantu nga 80% abalina COVID-19 balwadde obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, balina obulwadde obw'omu mpeke obuliko obubonero oba obutaliimu, era abasinga bawona.
Mu bantu nga 14%, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bweyongedde nnyo ne kiba nti kyetaagisa okubeera mu ddwaliro ate nga abantu abalala 6 ku buli kikumi balina obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaagisa okulabirirwa ennyo.
Omutindo gw'okufa kw'abalwadde abajjanjabirwa COVID-19 gwali gwa bitundu 4 ku buli 100.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twatunuulira engeri omuwendo gw'abantu abalina COVID-19 gye gukulaakulana mu buli ggwanga mu EU/EEA ne UK ne tugugeraageranya n'ogwa Hubei, China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne UK n'omu Italy wakati wa 31 January ne 15 March 2020.
Embeera za COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Oluvannyuma lw'ebyo ebyaliwo mu China, COVID-19 yeeyongera okusaasaana mu bitundu by'ensi era n'okulondawo ekkubo ery'okukwata ekirwadde kino mu nsi endala.
Nga 11 March 2020, Dayirekita wa WHO (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde.
