Mu EU/EEA, abantu abasatu abaasooka okukakasibwa obuwuka bwa COVID-19 mu Bufalansa baategeezebwa nga January 24, 2020 nga bavudde mu kibuga Wuhan, mu ssaza lya Hubei, mu China.
Nga 15 March 2020, abantu ba COVID-19 balabiddwa mu mawanga gonna 30 aga EU/EEA ne UK, era wakati wa 31 December 2019 okutuuka ku lunaku olwo, abantu 39,768 ne bafa 1,727 baalagiddwa, nga 17,750 ne bafa 1,441 mu Italy yokka.
