Embeera y'omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 mu EU/EEA ne UK yagoberera eya Hubei (China) (ekifaananyi 1).
Eri EU/EEA n'obutonde bwonna bwa UK, omuwendo gw'abantu abalina COVID-19 gwatandika okulinnya nga February 21, era ne gweyongera nnyo nga February 28, 2020 (ekirala).
Kino kyasinga kuva ku kwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa okuva mu Italy, naye buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne UK byalaga enkulaakulana y'omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye COVID-19 (ekirala).
