Mu butuufu, abalwadde abawona batera okuba n'omulwadde oyo mu musaayi gwabwe omuli obuwuka obuwerako obuziyiza obulwadde obwo.
Antibodies ze antibody globulin (AG) ekolebwa obutoffaali bwa lymphocyte B okulwanyisa obulwadde n'ebitundu ebirala eby'ebweru, era zimanya obuwuka obw'enjawulo mu bulwadde era ne buziwakanya butereevu.
Okusinziira ku kino, plasma yakuŋŋaanyizibwa okuva mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abaawona COVID-19 ne bagufumbira abalwadde 10 abalina embeera embi.
Bonna baayoleka obubonero obulungi mu ssaawa 24, nga bwe baayoleka obulwadde obutonotono, obuwuka obuli mu musaayi, n'okusaanuuka kw'omusaayi.
Kyokka, okukakasa n'okulaga obukakafu byetaagisa okusobola okukozesa enkola eno mu ngeri ey'enjawulo nga tetunnaba kufuna bujjanjabi.
Okugatta ku ekyo, olw'ebyo ebireetawo obujjanjabi, waliwo ebintu ebimu ebikyamu ebiva ku pulasima ebirina okwetegerezebwa.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuwuka obuyitibwa antibodies buyinza okuleetera omuntu okwekulumbaza ennyo n'aleeta obulwadde obuyitibwa cytokine release syndrome, obuyinza okuba obw'obulabe.
Obusinge bw'omubiri oguyitibwa antibody mu musaayi butera okuba obutonotono, era ne plasma eba eyetaagibwa nnyo okujjanjaba abalwadde abalina embeera enzibu.
Kizibu nnyo okuteekawo n'okufulumya eddagala erigema endwadde mu bwangu okusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde.
N'olwekyo, okuggya obutoffaali bwa B mu balwadde abawonye era n'okumanya ennamba y'obutonde ey'obutabaako buwuka oba okunoonyereza ku buwuka obutawaanya obuwuka, kisinga okuba eky'amaanyi.
Mu ngeri eyo, tusobola okwongera ku bungi bw'omubiri oguyitibwa antibody.
Eddagala ly'omu China ery'obuwangwa libadde likozesebwa okujjanjaba endwadde ez'enjawulo mu China okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka.
Kyokka, ebikolwa byayo byesigamye nnyo ku bintu bingi ebikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi obw'ekinnansi obw'omu China.
Ebintu ebisinga ebikola ku buwuka tebimanyiddwa oba tebitegeerekeka kubanga kizibu okubimenya n'okumanya obuwuka obwo oba enkola yabwo ennungi.
Mu kiseera kino, olw'obutaba na ddagala lyonna erisobola okujjanjaba COVID-19, eddagala ly'omu China lyafuuka ekimu ku bintu ebikulu eby'okujjanjaba abalwadde abalina obubonero obutonotono oba abo abawonye obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obujjanjabi bwa Shu Feng Ji Do ne Lian Hua King Wen bwazuulibwa nga bwa mugaso nnyo mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Ebisale ebisingawo eby'okuwona ku balwadde ba COVID-19 byalabikira mu bitundu bya China ebitali bimu ebyakozesanga eddagala lya China mu 87% ku balwadde baayo, omuli Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), ne Hunan (50%), ate nga ekitundu kya Hubei, ekikozesa eddagala lya China ery'obuwangwa kyokka nga kirimu abalwadde ba COVID-19 nga 30%, kyaliko ebisale ebisingawo okuba ebitonotono (13%).
Kyokka, kino kikwatagana bulungi kubanga waliwo ebintu ebirala bingi ebirina akakwate, gamba ng'omuwendo gw'abalwadde n'obuzibu bwabwe.
Nga 18 Febwali 2020, Paul Chang ne banne mu mulimu bafulumya okunoonyereza okwageraageranya eddagala ly'Ebugwanjuba (WM) ku ddwaliro erimu n'eddagala ly'Ebugwanjuba n'eddagala ly'omu China.
Baakizuula nti ekiseera eky'okuwona omusujja, obubonero okuggwaawo, n'okusigala mu ddwaliro kyali kitono nnyo mu bantu abajjanjabibwa eddagala ly'ebugwanjuba n'eddagala ly'omu China okusinga abo abajjanjabibwa eddagala ly'ebugwanjuba lyokka.
Ekisinga okwekwasa, omuwendo gw'obulwadde (obw'omulundi gumu n'obutono) gwali mutono nnyo mu kibiina kya Western Medicine + Traditional Chinese Medicine okusinga ekibiina kya Western Medicine yokka (7.4% ku 46.2%), era omuwendo gw'okufa gwali mutono nnyo mu kibiina kya Western Medicine + Traditional Chinese Medicine okusinga ekibiina kya Western Medicine yokka (8.8% ku 39%).
Kyokka, obutuufu n'obutuufu bw'eddagala ly'omu China likyalina okunoonyerezebwa mu bitundu ebirala.
Era kyandibadde kya ssanyu okunnyonnyola engeri gye bakolamu era n'okulaga engeri eddagala lya China gye lirina amaanyi oba engeri gye lirina okujjanjabirwamu.
Abalwadde abateeberezebwa okuba n'akawuka ka COVID-19 oba abakakasibwa nti balina akawuka kano batera okutya obulwadde obw'amaanyi, obuyitibwa COVID-19 era n'okufa.
Okugatta ku ekyo, obubonero bw'obulwadde obuyitibwa ssennyiga, obutaba na oxygen, n'okukoowa, awamu n'ebiva mu bujjanjabi, gamba ng'okuloota olw'okukozesa ennyo eddagala, biyinza okuleetera omuntu okweraliikirira n'okweraliikirira ennyo.
Mu kiseera kya SARS, abantu bangi baali balwadde nnyo, nga mw'otwalidde n'okweraliikirira, okweraliikirira, okutya, okwetulinkiriza, obulwadde bw'obwongo, okwegomba okw'okwerumya, n'okwegomba okw'okwerumya.
Okugoberera okuteekebwa mu mbeera ey'obutaba na bantu, ng'ekitundu ky'ebyobulamu mu bantu okwetegereza COVID-19, kiyinza okuleetera abantu okweraliikirira ennyo n'okuwulira obubi olw'obutafuna bulwadde, okweyawula ku bantu, n'okuvumisa ab'omu maka gaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
N'olwekyo, obujjanjabi bw'obwongo bulina okuweebwa abalwadde ba COVID-19, abantu abateeberezebwa okuba nga balina obulwadde, abantu abakolagana nabo, n'abantu abalala ababwetaaga.
Obuyambi bw'eby'omwoyo bulina okuzingiramu okussaawo ebibinja by'abasawo ab'enjawulo, enkuŋŋaana ez'okuwuliziganya n'abantu aba bulijjo n'obwegendereza ku buwuka bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'enteekateeka z'obujjanjabi, n'okukozesa ebyuma ebikugu n'ebikozesebwa okwewala okutabagana.
Okuzzaawo obulwadde obw'amaanyi okuggyawo akawuka okuva mu nsolo n'abantu abakwatibwa obulwadde okudda mu bantu abalina obulwadde buno kyetaagisa era emirundi mingi kijjanjabibwa n'eddagala erigema akawuka mu kulwanyisa kawuka ak'akawuka.
Kaweefube akoleddwa okuzimba eddagala eryesigamiziddwa ku protein S okuleeta obuwuka obutafaanana, obukola obulungi era obuwangaala n'obutaziyiza SARS-CoV.
Ensigo ez'obulamu ezirwadde eddagala lino zigezeseddwa mu by'ekika ky'ebisolo okujjanjaba SARS.
Kyokka, obukodyo bw'okulwanyisa obulwadde buno mu bantu abakaddiye, n'engeri gye bafiiramu, n'engeri gye bawonyaamu obulwadde bw'akawuka ka siriimu, tebannategeerekeka bulungi nga tetunnatandika kunoonyereza.
Kino kiyinza okuba nga kiva ku kuba nti SARS yaggwaawo emyaka 17 egiyise era okuva olwo tewali muntu yenna afunye obulwadde buno.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, abantu abamu ne MERS beeyongera okulabika mu bitundu by'omu masekkati ga Buwalabu era ne basaasaana mu bitundu ebirala olw'ensolo okweyongera okujja mu bitundu ebyo.
Enkola z'okulwanyisa MERS zaakolebwa nga bikozesa akawuka akatakyaliwo, plasma ezirimu omukka ogutawa kirimu (oxygen), abajjanjabi ba virus, nanoparticles, virus-like particles, n'ebitundu by'amagi agali mu protein, era ebimu byagezesebwa mu bisolo.
Okukulaakulanya eddagala eriruma era erikola obulungi erigema SARS-CoV-2 eri abantu abatalina bulwadde buno mulimu gwa bwangu era mukulu okufuga ekirwadde kino.
Kyokka, okuvvuunuka obuzibu buzibu olw'ekiseera ekiwanvu (emyezi 18 okutwalira awamu) ekyetaagisa okukulaakulanya eddagala n'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi ez'akawuka ka Corona.
COVID-19, ng'obulwadde obuggya, bwatandika okulaga enkola yaabwo mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abalwadde.
Mu mbeera ezisinga obungi, abalwadde basobola okuwona mpolampola nga tewali kibonerezo.
Kyokka, COVID-19, okufaananako SARS ne MERS, era ekwataganyizibwa n'ebisale eby'obulwadde n'okufa okw'amaanyi mu balwadde abakulu.
N'olwekyo, okuzimba ekyokulabirako ky'obulwadde obwesigika kikulu nnyo eri ebitongole by'obujjanjabi okussaawo obukulembeze mu buweereza bwabwe, naddala mu bitundu omuli obuzibu.
Okusinziira ku by'okuyiga ebibaddewo, ebintu bino wammanga biyinza okukwata oba okukwatagana n'okusuubira obulwadde mu balwadde ba COVID-19 (Laba Lukalala (Lukalala 33)):
Emyaka: Emyaka kye kintu ekisinga obukulu mu kutegeeza embeera ya SARS, era nga bwe kiri ne ku COVID-19.
Abantu abali wakati w'emyaka 30 ne 65 basinga kulwala COVID-19, nga 47.7% ku balwadde bano basukka emyaka 50 mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bantu 8,866 nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Abalwadde abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi baali basinga kulwala endwadde n'ebizibu era nga bakaddiye nnyo okusinga abo abataabwetaaga (mu bukadde bwa 66 ku 51) nga kino kiraga nti obukadde buyinza okuteebereza ku biva mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Ekika: SARS-CoV-2 yafuna abasajja bangi okusinga abakazi (0.31/100,000 vs. 0.27/100,000), nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Endwadde ez'olukalala n'ebizibu: Abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga okulabirirwa ennyo batera okufuna obulwadde bw'omutima n'okufuna obulwadde bw'omutima obutali bwenkanya.
Obulwadde bw'omutima era kye kyaviirako abantu okufa mu balwadde ba SARS.
Kigambibwa nti SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okukwata ku butoffaali bw'ekisenge kya zzaabu obulimu enzyme eyitibwa angiotensin-transferase 2, ekiyinza okuviirako obulwadde bw'ekibumba mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti obukadde n'obulwadde birina akakwate n'obumu era biyinza n'okusaanagana.
Ebivudde mu kukebera ebitalina mutawaana: Omuwendo gwa C-reactive protein (CRP) mu musaayi gukakasa obulumi bw'okusaakaanya oba obuvune mu bitundu by'omubiri, era kigambibwa nti guyinza okulangirira obulwadde, obujjanjabi, n'okuwona.
Enkolagana era yaleetebwawo wakati w'omutindo gwa C-reactive protein n'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 n'ebiseera by'obulamu.
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, okulinnya kwa LDH, AST, ALT, ne CK nabyo biyinza okuyamba mu kulabula.
Enzime zino ziraga nnyo mu bitundu bingi, naddala mu mutima ne mu kibumba, era zifuluma nga waliwo obuwuka obuvunda.
N'olwekyo, bino bye bifaananyi ebiraga obulemu mu mutima oba mu kifuba.
Obubonero obukulu obw'ekisawo: Okubala ekifuba n'okukulaakulana kw'obubonero bw'ekisawo awamu n'ebizibu ebirala birina okwekenneenyezebwa okusobola okuteebereza ebiva mu COVID-19 n'ebivaamu.
Okukozesa eddagala eriruma: Nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu, eddagala eruma omubiri lye litera okukozesebwa ng'eddagala eriyamba ku ndwadde ez'akawuka okukendeeza ku buzibu bw'obulwadde.
Okuva eddagala eryo bwe lyatandika okukozesebwa mu balwadde ba SARS, bangi ku abo abaawonawo ku bulwadde bwa SARS bafunye obulemu obw'olubeerera n'obulamu obutaggwaawo.
N'olwekyo, eddagala eririmu eddagala eririna okukozesebwa mu ddwaaliro eriri wansi era ery'akaseera katono mu balwadde ba COVID-19, bwe kiba kyetaagisa.
Okuzitoowererwa mu birowoozo: Nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu, mu kiseera kya COVID-19, abalwadde bangi baafuna obuzitoowererwa obw'amaanyi; batera okubeeranga mu mbeera ey'okwerinda okumala ekiseera ekiwanvu, obutebenkevu obw'amaanyi, era n'okufa kw'ab'eŋŋanda zaabwe n'abo be baali bakolagana nabo.
Okuwa amagezi n'okuyamba ab'obulwadde buno okumala ebbanga eritali lya wala kikulu nnyo okuyamba abalwadde bano okuwona obulumi n'okudda mu bulamu obwa bulijjo.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku bantu, COVID-19 kirabika erina endwadde ez'enjawulo ku SARS.
Ng'oggyeko okuzaala mu mputtu y'okuwummulamu, SARS-CoV-2 esobola okuzaala obulungi mu mputtu y'okuwummulamu ey'oku ntikko era n'eyinza okuleeta obubonero obutonotono oba obutabaamu bubonero bwonna mu kiseera eky'akawuka, nga bwe kiri ku bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe.
N'olwekyo, abalwadde abalina akawuka mu kiseera eky'obutandikiro oba mu kiseera ky'okulabirira abaana basobola okufulumya obuwumbi bwa kawuka mu mirimu gyabwe egy'olunaku, ne kiviirako obulwadde obutaba bwangu.
Kyokka, okusaasaanya akawuka ka SARS-CoV kyatwalibwanga nti kibaawo abalwadde bwe baba balwadde nnyo, ate ng'abasinga ku bantu abafuna akawuka tebafuna ku ddaala eryo.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 eyaliwo kati ya maanyi nnyo era nzibu okufuga okusinga SARS.
Kaakati China erina okufuba okw'amaanyi, omuli okuggya Wuhan n'ebibuga ebiriraanyeewo n'okusiba abantu bonna mu kifo ekyesudde, nga basuubira okulemesa SARS-CoV-2 okuyingira mu nsi.
Wadde ng'enteekateeka zino zikoze nnyo ku by'enfuna n'ebitundu ebirala eby'eggwanga, omuwendo gw'abalwadde abapya gukendeera, ekiraga nti obulwadde bukendedde.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa, ekirwadde kino kijja kukoma mu March era kijja kumala emyezi esatu oba ena.
Kyokka, waliwo abakugu abalala abatalina ssuubi ng'eryo.
Paul Hunter n'abalala baategeeza nti COVID-19, ekirabika ng'ekisukka mu SARS, tekigenda kuggwaawo mu 2020.
Ira Longini n'abalala baakola ekyokulabirako ekiraga nti SARS-CoV-2 esobola okukosa ebitundu bibiri ku bisatu eby'abantu mu nsi.
Ekibinja ky'abantu ab'omu Canada kyagamba nti SARS-CoV-2 yakeberebwa mu biwundu n'omumwa gw'abalwadde abaawonyezebwawo ne bava mu ddwaliro wiiki bbiri emabega, ekiraga nti akawuka kano akapya kaali kafuuka akawuka ak'omusujja gw'ensiri.
Wadde kiri kityo, obubonero obulaga nti abantu beeyongera okuzuula obulwadde buno mu China bulaga nti enkola eziriwo ziyinza okuba nga zikola.
Ebola yasoose kusuubirwa okuleeta obulwadde obukadde nga kimu n'ekitundu n'okufa.
Kyokka, obulwadde bwaggwaako nga bujjumbiddwa nga bagoberera enkola ez'amaanyi ez'okwerinda n'okweyawula.
Okufaananako SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 esobola okufuuka ekirwadde ekitasobola kusaasaanya era oluvannyuma ne kiggwaawo oba n'efuuka akawuka akataataataaganya abantu.
Wano wammanga waliwo okugeraageranya COVID-19 ne SARS ne MERS (ekifaananyi 55).
SARS-CoV-2 ekwattibwa ku kigero ekisingawo okuyita mu kukkuluma oba okusumulula, era esobola okusasaana n'okutuuka ku bintu ebirimu akawuka.
Obuwuka nabwo bwazuulibwa mu busajja, ekireetawo obusobozi obupya obw'okussa obuwuka mu busajja n'obutakka wansi.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bantu 138 kwalaga nti abantu 41 ku buli kikumi bayinza okuba nga baali bakozesezza endwadde mu ddwaliro, nga muno mwe muli abalwadde 17 abaalina obulwadde obulala era n'abalabirizi 40.
N'olwekyo, kyetaagisa okwegendereza ennyo okusobola okukuuma abantu, naddala abasawo, abakugu mu by'obulamu, ab'omu maka, bakozi bannaabwe, n'abo abaayita mu luguudo abaayita mu bantu abalina obulwadde.
Okwambala ebikozesebwa mu maaso kye kintu ekisooka ekikozesebwa okukendeeza ku bulabe bw'obulwadde; okukozesa ebikozesebwa mu nkola y'okulongoosa n'eby'okukozesa mu ngeri y'okuwummulamu (N95 series 1860s) biyamba mu kufuga okusaasaana kwa kawuka.
Bbalaza z'amaaso ez'okujjanjaba ziziyiza amataba g'omukka okuva mu muntu ayinza okuba n'obulwadde okuyingira mu mpewo oba okunywerera ku bintu, ne biyinza okuweebwa abalala.
Kyokka, masiki za N95 (serial 1860s) zokka ze zisobola okukuuma okuva ku kufukamira feriyoni entono ennyo wakati wa 10 ne 80 nm, nga feriyoni 5 ku buli kikumi zokka ze zisobola okuyingira ddala; SARS-CoV-2 efaanana ne SARS-CoV mu bunene era buli emu ya feriyoni nga 85 nm.
Olw'okuba obutoffaali busobola okuyita mu masiki etaano ez'okujjanjaba ezikuŋŋaanye, abasawo abakwatagana n'abalwadde balina okwambala masiki za N95 (serial 1860s) naye si masiki ez'okujjanjaba.
Ng'oggyeko obusozi, abasawo balina okwambala engoye ez'okweyawula ku balala okusobola okukendeeza ku bulabe bw'akawuka.
Obuwuka busobola n'okusaasaanya omuntu okuyita mu maaso.
Nga 22 January 2020, omusawo yafuna SARS-CoV-2 wadde nga yali ayambadde ekikookolo kya N95; oboolyawo akawuka kaayingira mu mubiri gwe okuyita mu maaso ge agaali gaakaaba.
N'olwekyo, abasawo balina okwambala ebikozesebwa mu kulwanyisa akawuka oba endabirwamu nga bakolera abalwadde.
Eri abantu bonna abali mu bitundu ebikoseddwa oba ebiyinza okukosebwa, kiragiddwa nnyo nti buli omu asalewo okuyonja engalo ze n'ensawo n'amazzi ag'okusaasaanya okusinga bwe kiba bulijjo, agezeeko okusigala awaka okweyawula ku balala era akendeeze ku nkolagana n'abantu abayinza okukosebwa.
Ekitundu kya ffuuti ssatu kiba kya kisa okusobola okukuuma abantu nga bali wala n'omulwadde.
Ebintu bino ngeri nnungi nnyo ey'okukendeeza ku kabi akali mu kusannyalala n'okutangira akawuka okusaasaana.
Wadde nga SARS-CoV-2 yajja mu nsi y'abantu ng'akawuka akapya, okufaananako kwayo okw'amaanyi ne SARS-CoV nga bwe kyalagibwa nga January 7, 2020 kyandibadde kiviiriddeko China okubeera mu mbeera ey'okweyimirizaawo okusinziira ku kujjukira okungi kwe yalina ku kawuka ka SARS mu 2003.
Kyokka, omukulu wa CDC mu Wuhan teyakakasa bantu okutuusa nga January 19, 2020 ng'agamba nti akawuka akapya kaaliko obuwuka obutono, nga tekasobola kusaasaana okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu era nga tewali buzibu bwa kukakaanya n'okukuuma obulwadde.
Obubaka buno bwaviirako abantu bonna obutaba beetegefu, naddala ng'eggwanga lyonna lyetegekera omukolo gw'omwaka ogujja, era nga kino kye kiseera ekikulu eky'okumalawo obulwadde mu Wuhan.
Ebitongole by'obufuzi eby'obufuzi mu China biyinza okuganyulwa mu kuyigirizibwa okwo okw'amaanyi era ne bikola enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, ebitongole bino birina (1) okuba eby'obwegendereza nga bifulumya obubaka eri abantu kubanga buli kigambo kikulu eri abantu era kisobola okukyusa enneeyisa n'okusalawo kwabwe; (2) okuba eby'obwegendereza n'okuddamu obubaka obutali bwa bulijjo okuva mu malwaliro mu kifo ky'okulindirira alipoota okuva eri abasawo oba abakungu; (3) okuba eby'obwegendereza okukwata kawumpuli mu kiseera ekisooka mu kifo ky'okufuba okubudaabuda abantu; (4) okuba eby'obwegendereza n'okufulumya ebikozesebwa ebikulu n'ebikwatagana n'obulwadde okusobola okwongera okulabirira abantu ku bulwadde obw'akawuka n'okukulaakulanya enkola y'okuddamu mu kitundu.
Obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obuva ku ssenyiga omukambwe SARS-CoV-2 bwatandika mu nkomerero ya December 2019.
Mu myezi ebiri gyokka, kyabunye mu China yonna ne mu nsi endala nga 50 mu kiseera kino.
Olw'okuba akawuka kalifaanana nnyo ne SARS-CoV era n'obubonero bwe bumu ne COVID-19 ne SARS, COVID-19 yaleetawo enneewulira y'okufuna obujanjabi bwa SARS.
Kyokka, waliwo enjawulo ez'amaanyi wakati wa COVID-19 ne SARS, nga zino nkulu nnyo okuziyiza ekirwadde n'okujjanjaba abalwadde.
COVID-19 ekosa abantu abakulu okusinga abato, abasajja okusinga abakazi, era n'obulwadde n'okufa nabyo bisingawo ku bakulu okusinga ku bavubuka.
SARS erina omuwendo gw'abantu abafa okusinga COVID-19 (10.91% nga bw'ogigeraageranya ku 1.44%).
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 basindika akawuka ne bwe baba nga tebalina bubonero, ate abalwadde ba SARS batera okukikola nga balwadde nnyo, ekireetera obuzibu okuziyiza COVID-19 okuva ku SARS.
Kino ky'ekimu ku by'ensonga lwaki SARS-CoV-2 yeeyongera okubuna n'obunyiikivu okusinga SARS-CoV.
Okugezesebwa kwa SARS-CoV-2 kuyinza okuba nga tekuli bulungi mu balwadde abamu aba COVID-19.
