N'ekisembayo, okuva ensolo nnyingi nga mw'otwalidde n'ebisolo eby'awaka bwe biyinza okuteeberezebwa okuba nga birina SARS-CoV-2, okulondoola n'okunoonyereza ku bulwadde byetaaga okukolebwa.
Ka kibe nti omulabirizi ye musota, musota oba ebisolo ebirala, SARS-CoV-2 oba obuwuka bwa kitaawe obuvaamu busobola okweyoleka nga bwe bufaanana mu bantu ababubeeramu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Okunoonyereza okw'omugaso mu kitundu kino kujja kulaga engeri SARS-CoV-2 gy'evuddewo mu bisolo, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebikolwa ebikulu eby'okutangira n'okuziyiza COVID-19 mu bantu.
Obwetaavu bw'okuddaabiriza emitindo gy'okunoonyereza ku COVID-19 "ey'okwekebera" ne "ey'okumanya".
Ku 6 Febwali 2020, ttiimu yaffe yafulumya obulagirizi obw'amangu ku kunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba akawuka ka coronavirus akaaliwo mu mwaka gwa 2019 (COVID-19), obwalaga obumanyirivu bwaffe era ne bukakasa nti waliwo obubaka obusaanidde okujjako mu kulwanyisa kawumpuli.
Wadde nga obulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) bulwadde bupya, okumanya kwaffe kweyongera okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'okugezesebwa mu ddwaliro; n'olwekyo enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba zeeyongera okuvuganyizibwa.
Mu bbaluwa eno, twaddamu ekyewuunyo ekyava mu bulagirizi bwaffe era ne tuwaayo ebisaanyizo eby'okunoonyereza ebipya, "omulwadde ateeberezebwa" ne "omulwadde ategeerekese", okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwa COVID-19 obw'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba (ebitabo omusanvu) ebyafulumizibwa akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka People's Republic of China.
Mu Ddesemba 2019, akawuka ka Corona akaakava mu bantu aka New Coronavirus 2019 (New Coronavirus 2019), kati akayitibwa obulwadde bwa Corona Virus 2019 (COVID-19) kaafuluma era akawuka kaako kayitibwa Corona Virus 2 nga kakwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Nga 11 March 2020, WHO yayita COVID-19 kawumpuli.
Okwewala ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yateekawo obulagirizi obw'amangu era ne bufulumizibwa ku mukutu gwa Internet mu lupapula lwa Military Medical Research nga Febwali 6, 2020.
Kyatwalibwa ng'ekikulu nnyo okuva lwe kyafulumizibwa.
Kyenva nkusaba weetegereze nti wadde nga COVID-19 kirwadde kipya, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kwe tulina kweyongera okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'okugezesebwa mu ddwaliro; era n'enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obulagirizi obukwata ku kuzuula n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 okuva mu National Health Commission of the People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn), bwafulumizibwa wakati wa January 16, 2020 ne March 3, 2020, nga bufulumidde mu nnamba musanvu nga waliwo enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi.
Kati, obulagirizi bwaffe buzzeemu okuddibwamu okuva eri Cho n'abalala, abaawa amagezi ag'obutereevu ag'okunoonyereza ku bubonero okusinziira ku kugezesebwa.
Okufuba kwabwe kwongedde obujulizi obupya mu bulagirizi bwaffe era ne bufuuka ekitabo eky'omugaso ennyo eri ekirwadde kino mu nsi yonna.
Tukkiriziganya n'okufuba kwabwe era tukusiima.
Kyokka, omulimu gwabwe gwetaaga okuddaabirizibwa okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwa COVID-19 obw'okunoonyereza n'obujjanjabi (empaka z'omulundi ogw'omusanvu) n'ebikugu ebivudde mu kunoonyereza.
Okusinziira ku kivvulu ky'omusanvu (March 3, 2020), okukakasa embeera ey'okwekengera kyetaaga okukwataganya ekintu kyonna ku bintu ebiri mu byafaayo by'obulwadde obw'obulwadde n'ebintu bibiri eby'obujjanjabi okusobola okutuuka ku kunoonyereza okujjuvu, oba kyetaaga okukakasa ebintu bisatu eby'obujjanjabi bw'oba tolina byafaayo bya bulwadde obumatiza:
Ebyafaayo by'obulwadde bw'ekirwadde: (1) Ebyafaayo omuli okutambula mu kibuga Wuhan n'ebitundu ebiriraanyewo, oba ebibiina ebirala ebyategeezezza nti birimu abantu abalina COVID-19, oba okubeera mu bitundu ebyo, mu nnaku 14 ez'oluvannyuma ng'obulwadde tebunnaba kutandika; (2) Ebyafaayo omuli okukwatagana n'abantu abalina obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 (nga balina ebibuuzo ebivaamu ebirungi ku DNA); (3) Ebyafaayo omuli okukwatagana n'abalwadde abalina omusujja oba obubonero bw'omukka okuva mu kibuga Wuhan, ebitundu ebiriraanyewo, oba ebibiina ebirala ebyategeezezza nti birimu abantu abalina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ez'oluvannyuma ng'obulwadde tebunnaba kutandika; (4) Ebyafaayo omuli okukwatagana n'abantu abalina obulwadde obumanyiddwa (nga 2 oba okusingawo) n'abantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi oba obubonero obutonotono, gamba ng'ab'omu maka oba mu bifo ebirala eby'omu ssomero, ebifo ebitonotono, oba eby'omu ofiisi.
Obulwadde: (1) omukka n'/oba obuwuka obuva mu mputtu z'omukka; (2) n'obubonero obulaga obulwadde bwa COVID-19; (3) okuba n'omuwendo gw'omusaayi oguli ku mutindo oguli mu mbeera nnungi, omutono ennyo, oba omutono ennyo ku muwendo gw'omusaayi mu kiseera eky'olubuto.
Okuzuula embeera ekakasibwa ku mbeera ey'okwekengera erina obujulizi bwonna obw'obulwadde oba obutakkaanya bw'omusaayi ku SARS-CoV-2 kulina kwesigamizibwa ku: (1) obubonero obw'omukisa obw'okunoonyereza ku PCR obw'ekiseera ekituufu ku SARS-CoV-2, (2) okukwatagana okw'amaanyi okw'enkula y'ensigo y'omusaayi n'obuntu bwa coronavirus ezimanyiddwa, (3) obubonero obw'omukisa obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi obw'omusaayi oguyitibwa IgM ne IgG, oba okuvvuunuka omusaayi gw'omusaayi oguyitibwa SARS-CoV-2 okuva ku mubi okudda ku IgG, oba okuba n'omusaayi oguli ku mutendera ogukwana oba okusinga emirundi ena.
Tulaba nti okugezesa kwa DNA mu kiseera ekituufu mu mputtu y'omukka oba mu musaayi kweyongedde mu nnamba ey'okubiri (Jjanwali 18, 2020) ne ey'okusatu (Jjanwali 22, 2020).
Okukebera obulwadde mu musaayi gw'omuntu kyongeddwa mu kivvulu eky'okuna (Jjanwali 27, 2020) ne eky'okutaano (Februwari 8, 2020); ate n'ekitabo ekirimu ebikolwa eby'omusaayi kyongeddwa mu kivvulu eky'omusanvu.
Enkyukakyuka zino zaesigamye ku mulimu gw'abanoonyereza ogugenda mu maaso okuteekateeka enkola y'ebikozesebwa eby'okunoonyereza ku DNA okusobola okunoonyereza amangu, awamu n'ebitundu by'omukka ogw'okufuuyira omuli n'eby'omusaayi, ekireeseewo okuzuula ebitundu eby'enjawulo, n'okuyamba okuteekawo obubonero bw'omubiri ogumu ku mbeera eziriwo.
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, waliwo obujulizi bungi obulaga nti tulina okwegendereza nga tukola n'abalwadde abalina obubonero obutali bwa bulijjo n'abo abatalina bubonero.
N'olwekyo, obubaka obuli mu kipande kya Cho n'abalala, bwe balina okuteeka ku muntu ataliiko bubonero, balina okubukyusa.
Enkola y'okukebera ebipimo nayo yeetaaga okukakasibwa mu nkola n'okunoonyereza okulala.
Mu nkomerero, tusuubira okufuna obujulizi obulala era tukubiriza abasomi okutuwa endowooza zaabwe.
Okukebera "omulwadde ategeerekese" n'omulwadde ategeerekese, tukubiriza okugoberera n'okugoberera obulagirizi obuggya obuva mu mawanga abantu mwe babeera.
Ekibinja kyaffe era kijja kuddamu okuteekateeka obulagirizi bwaffe mu kiseera ekituufu.
Bangladesh erangiridde abantu bataano abafa COVID-19, omuwendo ogusinga obunene buli lunaku
Bangladesh eggulo yakakasa okufa kwa COVID-19 okuwera abataano ku lunaku olwo.
Guno gwe muwendo ogusingawo ogw'abantu abafa omulundi gumu olw'akawuka kano.
Ekitongole kya Bangladesh ekikola ku by'obujjanjabi, okufuga n'okunoonyereza ku ndwadde (IEDCR) kyagamba nti, okutuusa eggulo, abantu 114 be balabiddwa nga balwadde ate 33 be bawonyezebwawo nga bali waka.
