Akulira ekitongole kya Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research, Dr. Mirjadi Sabrina Flora, yategeezezza mu lukungaana lwa bannamawulire ku mukutu gwa Intaneeti nti abafudde bana abasajja ate omu mukazi.
Okusinziira ku Dr. Mirjadi, waaliwo abalwadde babiri abasukka mu myaka 60, abalwadde babiri wakati w'emyaka 51 ne 60, n'omulwadde omu wakati w'emyaka 41 ne 50.
