Entegeka ya Interaction yategeeza nti gavumenti ya China yawaayo amasiki 200,000 eri Philippines nga Febwali 6, oluvannyuma lwa Ssenateri Richard Gordon okutwala amasiki obukadde 3.16 mu Wuhan.
