Japan yawaayo amasiki agawerera ddala omuwendo gwa bukadde mu Wuhan, Turkey yatuma ebyuma eby'ekisawo, Russia yatuma obuwumbi obusukka mu 13 obw'ebikozesebwa mu Wuhan, Malaysia yalangirira okuwaayo engalo z'ekisawo obukadde 18 mu China, Germany yawaayo eby'okukozesa eby'ekisawo nga mw'otwalidde n'ebikozesebwa eby'okwerinda 10,000, Amerika yawaayo obuwumbi 17.8 obw'eby'okukozesa eby'ekisawo mu China, era yasuubiza okuwa obuyambi obulala bwa doola obukadde 100 eri amawanga agaakosebwa.
