Omusuubuzi Jack Ma yatuma mu Addis Ababa, Ethiopia obukadde 1.1 bw'ebikopo, obukadde 6 bw'ebikoikooti, n'ebikooti 60,000 eby'okwerinda, era nga bitwalibwa mu Uganda.
Oluvannyuma yatuma mu Panama ebikozesebwa mu kukebera abantu 5,000, ebikozesebwa mu kusikka abantu 100,000, n'ebikozesebwa mu kufumiitiriza.
Uganda era yawaayo obuyambi eri Canada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, ne Czech Republic baalaga nti beeraliikirivu olw'amasiki n'ebikozesebwa mu kufuba ebyakolebwa mu China.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, Spain yakyusawo ebitundu 58,000 eby'ebigezo bya Corona okuva mu China ebyali bituufu ebitundu 30 ku buli kikumi, ate mu kiseera kye kimu, Netherlands yakomyawo ebitundu 600,000 eby'ebigezo ebyakolebwa mu China ebyali ebikyamu.
