Okugezesebwa mu laboratory ku bulwadde bwa coronavirus obw'okuwummulamu 2019 (COVID-19) ne SARS-CoV-2 kuzingiramu engeri z'okumanya obuwuka nga bw'okimanya obuwuka obuleeta obuwuka.
RT-PCR ekakasa nti waliwo akawuka mu bibala, nga ekakasa DNA ya corona.
Kino kikeberebwa bulungi era kyakolebwa okukebera ddagala lya SARS-CoV-2 lyokka.
Kikozesebwa okukakasa obulwadde obubaddewo oba obubaddewo.
Okuzuula ebitundu by'omubiri ebiziyiza obulwadde (antitotoxicology) kukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza n'okwetegereza abantu.
Okugezesebwa kw'omubiri kulaga abantu bameka abafunye obulwadde, nga mw'otwalidde n'abo abalina obubonero obutonotono obutasobola kwogerwako oba abatalina bubonero.
Okufa kw'obulwadde n'omutindo gw'omubiri ogukugira obulwadde mu bantu bisobola okussibwako essira okusinziira ku bibala by'okugezesebwa kuno.
Olw'okuba ebikeberebwa bitono, tewali ggwanga lyonna mu Maaki 2020 eryalina obubaka obwesigika ku kusaasaanya akawuka mu bantu baalyo.
Nga 23 March, tewali ggwanga lyonna eryakebera bantu baalyo abasukka mu 3%, era waliwo enjawulo mu bungi bw'okugezesebwa mu mawanga ag'enjawulo.
Enjawulo eno era esobola okubaako kye kikola ku kufa kw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa, mu nsi ezimu okuteeberezebwa ennyo.
Okukozesa RT-PCR, ebifaananyi eby'omukka ebiggiddwa mu ngeri ezitali zimu, gamba ng'omukka gw'omu nnyindo oba ekika ky'ekinnansi, bisobola okwekebejjebwa.
Ebyava mu kunoonyereza bibaawo mu ssaawa ntono oba ennaku bbiri.
RT-PCR ekozesebwa mu kujjanjaba mu bulago teyeesigama ku ddwaaliro ly'omulwadde okutuusa wiiki esooka.
Omusaayi guyinza okuggibwa mu bulago nga bwe gweyongera okugaziya mu biwundu.
Abantu abalina obulwadde buno abagezeddwa mu wiiki ey'okubiri, mu kifo ky'ekyo, bayinza okukebera mu nnyindo zaabwe nga bakozesa kateterero oba enkola ey'okukooyesa.
Ekimu ku bigezo bya PCR ebyasooka kyatandikibwawo mu January 2020 mu Charité e Berlin nga bikozesa polymerase instantaneous sequential reverse transcription (RT-PCR), era kyafuuka omusingi gw'ebikozesebwa 250,000 eby'okugezesa ebyasaasaasaanyizibwa ekitongole kya World Health Organization (WHO).
UK nayo yatandikawo ekigezo nga 23 January 2020. Kampani ya South Korea Kogenebiotech yatandikawo PowerChek Coronavirus kit ekituufu eky'okukozesa mu ddwaaliro era nga kyesigamye ku PCR nga 28 January 2020.
Okunoonya ekika kya "E" ekisangibwa ku kookoloona eza beta ne RdRp eza SARS-CoV-2. Mu China, BGI Group kye kimu ku bizinensi ezisoose okufuna olukusa okuva mu China National Medical Products Administration olw'okukozesa eddagala eriyamba okunoonyereza ku SARS-CoV-2 nga lyesigama ku PCR. Mu Amerika, ekitongole kya CDC kigaba ekika kyabwo ekya COVID-19 ekyesigamye ku RT-PCR mu malaalo g'ebyobulamu nga kiyita mu International Detection Materials Supply Agency.
Ekimu ku bikeberebwa ebisatu eby'ekika mu bitabo eby'edda eby'ebigezo byavaamu ebivudde mu bukyamu olw'ebirungo ebikyamu, era ekimu ku bikeberebwa kyalwawo nnyo mu CDC mu Atlanta; kino kyaviirako okukebera ebipimo ebitonotono nga 100 buli lunaku okuggwa obulungi mu mwezi gwa Febwali 2020.
Okugeza, ebigezo ebikozesa ebitundu bibiri tebyaweebwa bukakafu okutuusa nga Febwali 28, 2020, era n'okutuusa olwo, laboratories za gavumenti n'ez'omu kitundu tezaali zikkirizibwa kutandika kugezesa.
FDA yakkiriza okugezesebwa kuno wansi w'okukkiriza okukozesa mu bwangu. Ab'eddagala mu Amerika baatandika okugezesa mu matandika ga March 2020.
Nga March 5, 2020, LabCorp yalangirira nti okugezesa kwa COVID-19 okusinziira ku RT-PCR kujja kubaawo mu ggwanga lyonna.
Mu ngeri y'emu, Quest Diagnostics yafulumya okugezesebwa kwa COVID-19 mu ggwanga lyonna okuva nga Maaki 9, 2020.
Tewali kkomo ku bungi bw'ebirungo; ebibala birina okuggibwawo n'okukolebwako okusinziira ku biragiro bya CDC.
Mu Russia, ekitongole kya State Center for Virology and Biotechnology Research kyakola era ne kifulumya Victor COVID-19 test.
Nga Febwali 11, 2020, FHS yawandiisa ekigezo. Nga Maaki 12, 2020, kyalagibwa nti Mayo Clinic yali ekoze ekigezo ekikebera obulwadde bwa COVID-19. Nga Maaki 13, 2020, Roche Diagnostics yafuna olukusa okuva ku FDA olw'ekigezo ekiyinza okukolebwa mu ssaawa 3.5 ku bungi obunene, ekikkiriza ekyuma kimu okukola ebigezo nga 4,128 mu ssaawa 24.
Nga 19 March 2020, FDA yawa Abbott Laboratories olukusa olw'okukozesa mu bwangu (EUA) okukola okugezesa ku Abbott m2000; eddagala lino lyaweebwa olukusa olufaanana ku Hologic, Lap Corp, ne Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Nga 21 March 2020, Sifid yafuna olukusa olw'omutawaana okuva mu FDA olw'okugezesebwa okw'eddakiika nga 45.
FDA yakkiriza okugezesa okukozesa enkola ey'okunyweza DNA mu kifo kya PCR.
Olw'okuba tekyetaagisa kuzitoowereranga, enkola eno esobola okuleeta ebibala mu ddakiika nga ttaano n'ebibala mu ddakiika nga 13.
Mu kiseera kino waliwo ebyuma nga 18,000 mu Amerika era Abbott asuubira okwongera ku mulimu gw'okunoonyereza okukola ebigezo 50,000 buli lunaku. Taiwan era ekulaakulanya ekigezo ekikozesa ekirwadde ekirina ekika kimu ekikwatagana n'ekika kya Corona virus, mu ssuubi nti kisobola okuleeta ebivudde mu ddakiika 15 oba 20 nga ekigezo ky'omukka ekyangu.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu March 2020 kwalaga nti "ebifaananyi by'omutima tebirina mugaso gwa maanyi mu kulabula mu mitendera egyasooka, ate ebiva mu CT [Ct] biyinza okuba nga birabika bulungi ng'obulwadde tebunnaba kulabika".
Ebintu ebitera okulabikira mu CT mulimu ebiragala eby'amabala ebiri ku njuyi bbiri, ebirina ebitundu bingi, nga biriko enjuyi ezitali zimu n'ebisenge bya mugongo.
Obulwadde buno bweyongera bweyongera n'obutaba bulungi.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu kibuga Wuhan okwageraageranya PCR ne CT ku nsibuko y'ekirwadde kino, kwalaga nti CT esobola okuba ey'obulabe okusinga PCR, wadde nga si nnungi, ng'ebitundu byayo bingi ebiraga ebifaananyi bikontana n'obulwadde bwa pulmonary ne mu mbeera endala.
Mu March 2020, American College of Radiology yakubiriza "obutakozesa CT okukebera COVID-19 oba okugitwala ng'ekikebera ekisooka ekiragira obulwadde". Mu March 2020, CDC yakubiriza okukozesa PCR ng'ekikebera ekisooka.
Ekimu ku bikolwa eby'omubiri okuziyiza obulwadde kwe kufulumya ebitundu eby'omubiri ebiziyiza obulwadde, omuli IgM ne IgG.
Zisobola okukozesebwa mu kuzuula obulwadde mu bantu okuva ku nnaku 7 oba oluvannyuma lw'okwoleka obubonero, okumanya obusobozi bw'omubiri, n'okwetegereza abantu. Ebigezo biyinza okukolebwa mu laboratories ez'enjawulo (CLT) oba nga bigezesebwa ku bifo eby'obujjanjabi (POCT).
Obukodyo obukozesebwa mu by'ekisawo obuyinza okukola ebintu bino mu laboratory nnyingi, naye obukodyo obwo businziira ku ngeri buli nkola gy'eyinza okufunamu.
Mu bifo eby'enjawulo, ekitundu kimu eky'omusaayi oguli mu bitundu by'omubiri kye kikozesebwa, wadde nga n'ebitundu ebirala bisobola okukozesebwa okulondoola obulwadde.
Okukebera ku kifo ekikuumibwa abalwadde, omusaayi gumu gufulumizibwa mu kifuba.
Okwawukana ku nkola ya PCR, tekyetaagisa kukola kintu kyonna nga tonnakebera. Nga March 26, 2020, FDA yalonda abantu 29 abaategeezezza ekitongole ekyo nga bwe kyali kyetaagisa, era abasobola okugaba ebikebera by'omubiri.
Nga 7 omwezi gwa April, 2020, FDA yakkiriza ekigezo kimu kyokka wansi w'okukkiriza okukozesebwa mu mbeera y'obudde obw'amangu. Mu nkomerero ya March, 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics ne Epitope Diagnostics zaafuna obukkiriza bwa Bulaaya ku byuma byabwe eby'okugezesa, ebiyinza okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa IgG ne IgA mu musaayi.
Okugezesa kuno kukola ebipimo bikumi na bikumi mu ssaawa ntono era nga kuno kwangu nnyo okusinga PCR eya bulijjo ey'obusawo bwa RNA.
Obuwuka buno busobola okuzuulibwa oluvannyuma lw'ennaku 14 ng'omuntu amaze okufuna obulwadde. Mu April, Bungereza yakizuula nti ebikozesebwa mu kukebera obulwadde obwo byali tebirina mugaso gwonna.
Hong Kong erina enteekateeka ey'abalwadde abakwatibwa obulwadde obw'obulabe okusigala mu maka gaabwe, "ekisenge ky'obudde obw'amangu okuwa abalwadde obuwuka obw'omulembe", okufuka amalusu mu buweke, n'okubuzzaayo okufuna ebivudde mu kukebera oluvannyuma lw'ekiseera kitono. Ekitongole kya NHS kya Bungereza kigamba nti kigezaako enteekateeka ey'okugezesa abantu abakwatibwa obulwadde obw'obulabe mu maka gaabwe, ekikugira abantu abalina obulwadde okugaziya obulwadde nga bazze mu ddwaliro oba obwetaavu bw'okusaanyaawo emmotoka ey'eddwaliro.
Ebitongole ebikola ku by'okwekebeza mu mmotoka mu South Korea bisobodde okukola ebigezo ebyangu era ebingi mu nsi yonna. Mu Bugirimaani, ekibiina kya National Association of Medical Forensic Insurers kyagamba nga March 2 nti kisobodde okukola ebigezo nga 12,000 buli lunaku ku balwadde abava mu ddwaliro era abantu 10,700 be baakezesebwa mu wiiki ewedde.
Ssente z'okujjanjaba omuntu zibalibwa omusawo bw'aba alagidde okugezesebwa.
Okusinziira ku mukulembeze w'ekitongole kya Robert Koch, Bugirimaani erina obusobozi bw'okunoonyereza obukadde 160,000 buli wiiki.
Nga 19 March, ebigezo by'obulabe mu mmotoka byaggulwawo mu bibuga ebinene.
Nga 26 Maaki 2020, omuwendo gw'ebigezo ebyakolebwa mu Bugirimaani tegwali gumanyiddwa, kubanga ebyavudde mu bigezo ebyo byabadde birungi byokka.
Okunoonyereza okwasooka kwalaga nti okuva mu wiiki y'omwaka 12/2020, ebitundu 483,295 byateekebwako ebigezo okutuusa ku nkomerero ya wiiki 12/2020, era ebitundu 33,491 (6.9%) byazuulibwa nga birimu akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2. Mu Isiraeri, abanoonyereza ku ttenkoni ne mu ddwaliro lya Rambam baakola enkola ey'okunoonyereza ku byokulabirako ebyaggibwa mu balwadde 64 mu kiseera kye kimu era ne babigezesa, nga bakuŋŋaanya ebifaananyi era nga tebayongera kunoonyereza okuggyako ng'ekifaananyi ekikuŋŋaanyiziddwa kizuuliddwa nga kirimu akawuka. Mu Wuhan, BGI yafulumya laboratory ey'ekiseera ey'okunoonyereza ku by'obudde obw'amangu nga erina ekifo ekiriko ebifaananyi 2,000 ekiyitibwa "Yan-Huo Eye" (Fuo Fire Eye, oba "Enjuba 5", mu Luwalabu) esobola okuzuula ebifaananyi ebisukka mu 10,000 mu 2020.
Wang Jian, omutandisi wa BGI, bwe yalabirira omulimu gw'okuzimba era nga kyamala ennaku ttaano, ebyokulabirako byalaga nti obulwadde mu Hubei bwandibadde bukula 47% era nga n'ebbeeyi y'okwerinda egenda kweyongera emirundi ebiri singa obuyinza bw'okukebera obwo tebutuukirizibwa.
Wuhan Lab yagoberera n'okuteekawo Huo-Yan Labs mu Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, Shanghai, n'ebibuga 12 mu China yonna.
Nga March 4, 2020, obubala obwa buli lunaku bwali 50,000 buli lunaku. Origami Assays yafulumya ebiwandiiko ebiggya era ebikubisaamu enkuŋŋaana ebiyinza okukebera abalwadde 1,122 okukebera COVID-19 nga bakozesa ebiwandiiko 93 byokka.
Mu March, obutaliimu bwa bubonero n'obutakola bulungi byaleetawo obuzibu mu kufuba okw'amaanyi mu Bulaaya, Bungereza ne Amerika.
Kino kyaleetera abakugu abamu okunoonyereza ku nkola z'okwetegekera ebibala omuli okufumita ebibala ku 98 °C (208 °F) okumala eddakiika 5 okuggya mu RNA okusobola okukola ebigezo ebirala. Nga Maaki 31, kyalagulwa nti UAE eri ku ntikko y'ensi mu kugezesa abantu baayo ku kirwadde kya coronavirus era eri ku kkubo ery'okuzzaawo omutindo gw'okugezesa abantu abasinga obungi.
Kino kyakolebwa nga tukozesa obusobozi bw'okugezesa mu mmotoka, era nga tugula laboratory ey'obugagga obujjuvu okuva mu Group 42 ne BGI (nga bagoberera laboratories zaabwe eza "Huo-Yan" mu China).
Ekimera kino kyateekebwawo mu nnaku 14 zokka, era kisobola okukola enkumi n'enkumi z'ebigezo bya RT-PCR buli lunaku era kye ky'ekikopo ekisooka mu nsi yonna eky'obunene buno nga kikozesebwa ebweru wa China.
Enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okugezesa eziragira ebitundu eby'enjawulo eby'obusika bwa coronavirus zaakolebwa mu China, Bufalansa, Bugirimaani, Hong Kong, Japan ne Amerika.
Ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu (WHO) kyakola enteekateeka y'Olubulaniya ey'okuleeta ebyuma ebiyamba abantu abava mu mawanga agatali ba ssente nnyingi.
Enteekateeka y'e Bugirimaani yatangaazibwa nga January 17, 2020; enkola eyaleetebwawo ekitongole kya CDC mu Amerika yali teriiwo okutuusa nga January 28, ekireetera okuwera okugezesebwa okuliwo mu Amerika. China ne Amerika zaaliko ebizibu ku ngeri ebigezo gye byesigika mu kiseera eky'olubuto, era ensi zino zombi ne Australia zaali tezisobola kuwa bantu ebigezo bimala okutuukiriza ebisaanyizo n'okugoberera amagezi g'abakugu mu by'obulamu.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, abakugu bagamba nti okugezesebwa mu bungi mu South Korea kiyambye okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa coronavirus.
Gavumenti ya South Korea eyongedde amaanyi mu kugezesa mu laboratories ez'obwannannyini okumala emyaka mingi.
Nga 16 March, WHO yasabye okwongera ku nteekateeka z'okugezesa ng'ekigendererwa ekisinga obulungi okukendeeza ku COVID-19. Okweyongerayongera kw'okugezesebwa okuva ku buwumbi n'obuwumbi bw'akawuka ka virus kuleetedde enkumi n'enkumi z'okugezesebwa okujjula mu laboratories ez'obwannannyini mu Amerika, era n'okuteekebwa kw'ebikebera n'ebirungo eby'obutwa okuvumbulwa.
Mu March 2020, China yategeeza nti waliwo obuzibu mu bukakafu bw'ebikozesebwa mu kukebera.
Mu Amerika, ebigezo bya CDC byazuulibwa nga "bitali birungi"; gavumenti n'evaako obuzibu obw'obulabirizi obwali bulemesa okugezesebwa mu ngeri ey'enjawulo. Spain yagula ebigezo okuva mu kkampuni y'omu China eyitibwa Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Ltd, naye n'ekizuula nti ebyavaamu tebyali bituufu.
Kkampuni yategezezza nti ebivudde mu kunoonyereza ebyo biyinza okuba nga byava ku butali butuukirivu mu kukuŋŋaanya ebibala oba nga tebikozesezza bulungi.
Minisitule ya Spain yagamba nti ejja kuddamu okugula ebikozesebwa ebirimu ebizuuliddwa ebikyamu, era nti ejja kubizzaawo n'ebikozesebwa ebirala okuva mu Shenzhen Bioeasy.
Katikkiro Matovic yasalawo okugisuulira mu mugga Danube. Prof. Ahmet Kara ow'omu minisitule y'ebyobulamu mu Turkey yategeezezza nti ebigezo bya Turkey bye yagula okuva mu China byali "n'obubonero obw'obutali butuukirivu" era "byasibibwa".
