Enzimu ya ACE2 ekwata ku bitundu by'omubiri eby'ebweru (ebisenge by'omubiri) mu busaayi, emisulo, omutima, ensigo, n'ebisenge.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 evuganya omulimu gwa angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) nga ekendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin 2 n'okwongera ku angiotensin (1-7); ekireetera okuba eddagala eryasuubizibwa mu bujjanjabi bw'endwadde z'omutima n'omusaayi. Era y'engeri ezimu ez'obutwa bwa coronaviruses okuyingira mu mubiri.
Ensaano y'omuntu ey'enzamu eno eyitibwa hACE2.
Enzimu eyitibwa angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 erina zinc era esangibwa ku maaso ga obutoffaali bw'omubiri.
Ensawo ya angiotensin 2 erina enzyme enfuufu eyitibwa M2 peptidase erina amine end, ne colectrine carboxyl end.
Enzimu ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ye proteini eya membrane eya type 1, era erina enzyme ez'omugaso eziri ku maaso g'obutoffaali bw'omutima n'ebitundu ebirala eby'omubiri.
Ekitundu eky'ebweru w'omubiri ekikola ku angiotensin 2 kiwandikawo ekitundu ekirala ekikola ku lususu nga kiriko ekika ky'ensulo ekiyitibwa shidases, ekireeta protein esobola okuvunda mu musaayi n'okufuluma mu nsawo.
Enzimu eno eyitibwa angiotensin-2 eri mu bitundu by'omubiri ebisinga obungi: ekwatagana n'ebisenge by'omubiri eby'obutoffaali obwa type 2 mu biwundu, mu butoffaali bw'omubiri obw'omu bulago obutonotono, mu butoffaali bw'omubiri obw'omu nsingo n'omubiri gw'omuntu, era ne mu butoffaali bw'omubiri obwesigamiziddwa ku bisenge by'omubiri mu bitundu ebisinga obungi.
DNA erya RNA, ekikakasa nti angiotensin 2 ekyusiddwa, eri mu bwongo, mu kiwato, wansi w'omutwe, ne mu kiwato.
Omulimu omukulu ogwa angiotensin-2 kwe kukola ng'omutunzi wa angiotensin.
Enzimu eno ekubiriza enkola ya angiotensin 1 okufuuka angiotensin 2.
Mu ngeri y'emu, enzyme eyisa ensimbi ya angiotensin 2 esobola okuggyawo ensimbi ya angiotensin 2 (aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine) n'egikyusa n'efuuka angiotensin (1-7), (histidine-aspartate-arginine-phenylalanine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine).
Enzimu eno ekyusa angiotensin 2 n'eyonoona ensimbi endala okuli [des-arginine9] - bradykenin, aplin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, ne gerlin.
Enzimu ya angiotensin 2 era ekubiriza entambula y'ensiri y'omusawo wa amino acid SLC6A19, era erina ekifo mu bulwadde bwa Hartt.
Enzimu ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2, ng'obutonde obuyitibwa transmembrane, y'eyingira mu butoffaali bwa koronavirusi ezimu, omuli omuntu eya NR63, SARS-CoV (akawuka akooleka akawuka ka SARS), ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akooleka obulwadde bwa COVID-19).
Naddala, okukwatagana kwa S1 ne Sars-CoV-2 ne enzyme ya angiotensin 2 ku lususu lw'omubiri kuleetawo okukwata omubiri n'okusaasaanya akawuka n'enzyme mu bitundu by'omubiri.
Enkola eno ey'okuteekawo erina okuteekawo protein S nga enzyme ya protease ey'omu lususu, Serin2 eya musoke, era nga ekirwadde kino kikyali mu kugezesebwa ng'obujjanjabi. Kino kireetera abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa enzyme eya angiotensin 2 mu mubiri kiyinza okuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina bingi eby'enjawulo n'ebitongole ebikola ku by'obulamu biwagira okukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors (ACIs) n'eryitibwa angiotensin receptor blockers.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa n'okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku July 11, 2012 kwalaga nti "okukozesa enzibu za angiotensin-converting enzyme (ATC) kwaliko okukendeera okw'amaanyi mu kabi k'obulwadde bwa pulmonary by'okunafuwa ku 34% bw'okugeraageranya ku bantu ab'omugaso".
Ate era, "obubenje bw'obulwadde bwa luponeoni bwagenda bukendeera mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa eddagala eriyitibwa angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors, era abo abaalina obulwadde bwa luponeoni, naddala abo abalina obulwadde bw'omutima oba obulwadde bw'omutima.
Okukozesa enziyiza za angiotensin-converting enzyme (ECT) kyaviirako okufa okuva mu bulwadde bwa pulmonary disease, wadde ng'ebyo ebyavaamu byali bya wansi nnyo bw'obigeraageranya ku kabi akali mu bulwadde bwa pulmonary disease".
Enzimu ya rhACE2 ekkirizibwa okuba eddagala eriggya eri obulwadde bw'amawuggwe. Kigambibwa nti erongoosa omusaayi gw'omu mawuggwe era n'okusaasaanya omukka gwa oxygen mu mbizzi ezirina obulwadde bw'okufuna obuwuka obuyitibwa multiple-fat diabetes.
Enzimu ya angiotensin 2 erina ekitundu ky'ekiseera eky'obulamu obutonotono eky'essaawa nga 10, era etandika okukola oluvannyuma lw'eddakiika 30, era n'ebiseera byayo eby'okukola bisobola okuweza essaawa 24.
Waliwo obujulizi bungi obulaga nti angiotensin-2 eyinza okuba obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi eri abo abalina obutali bugumiikiriza ku eddagala eriyitibwa RAS, era n'obulwadde obuli mu musaayi omungi. Waliwo ebigezo mu ddwaaliro ebikebera ku ngeri y'okuteeka enzijanjaba ya angiotensin-2 mu bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde bwa buwuka obw'okubudaabuda.
Enkola za COVID-19 zikozesebwa mu programu ez'oku ssimu ezikoleddwa okuyamba mu kulabirira abantu abakwatiddwa obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19), kwe kugamba, okumanya abantu ("abakwatiddwa") abayinza okuba nga baakwatagana n'omuntu alina obulwadde.
Enkola nnyingi zaakolebwa oba zaaweebwa obuyambi bwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu.
Waliwo enkola nnyingi ezikozesebwa mu kukola programu ez'okunoonya abo be tuwuliziganya nabo.
Bangi baalaze okutya ku by'obuntu, naddala ku nkola ezisinziira ku kutegeera ebifo abakozesa programu gye bali.
Enkyusa ezitali za bukuumi zizingiramu okukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa okuva ku ssimu endala.
Nga 10 omwezi gwa 2020 nga April, Google ne Apple baalangirira nti baali bayingiddewo enkola ey'okuyamba programu zino ezikozesa Bluetooth, mu nkola zaabwe ez'okuweereza Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti ya China, ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, yatandikawo programu esobozesa abantu okukebera oba nga baatuukiddwako abantu abalina COVID-19.
Ye app abantu gye bakozesa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 mu China. Mu Singapore, abantu bakozesa app eyitibwa TraceTogether.
Ekibiina ky'eby'obufuzi ekya ICT kyakola ku nkola eno, ne kifulumya nga app ya Open Source era egenda kuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yatandikawo app ya "StopKorona", ey'okuteeka ku Bluetooth okugoberera abantu abalina obulwadde n'okuyamba ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu.
Minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'entekinologiya ekolagana ne minisitule y'ebyobulamu mu kutondawo programu.
Nga 14 April 2020, programu yali ekyalinda okukkirizibwa ku Google Play Store ne ku Apple App Store.
Nga 12 omwezi gwa April, gavumenti yategeeza nti app ey'okunoonyereza ku bantu abafaanana nga bano yali mu mbeera ey'amaanyi era nga esobola okuweebwa abantu mu wiiki ntono. Ireland ne Bufalansa zirina enteekateeka ez'okutandikawo app efaanana bw'etyo, eyitibwa "StopCovid".
Australia ne New Zealand zombi zirowooza ku kutandikawo programu ezinyweza TraceTogether eya Singapore, era ne BlueTres.TN protocol Russia eteekateeka okutandikawo programu ekozesa geospatial eya balwadde abagambibwa okuba nga balina COVID-19 okuva mu batuuze b'e Moscow, nga eno eteekeddwa okukakasa nti tebasimbula maka gaabwe.
Ross Anderson, profesa wa by'obukuumi mu yunivasite ya Cambridge, ayogedde ku bizibu bingi ebiyinza okubaawo mu nkola eziriko enkola ezikozesebwa mu nkola, omuli obuzibu obuyinza okuvaamu singa enkola ezo zikozesebwa abantu abatono.
Okukola ku kweraliikirira ku kubuna kwa programu ez'obukuusa oba ez'obulabe, Apple eremesezza ebibiina by'abantu okuteekawo enkola ezikwata ku bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe mu tterekero lyabyo.
Google ne Amazon nabyo byateekawo amateeka ge gamu.
Abakulembeze b'obwannannyini baalaze okutya ku biva mu kukozesa programu za coronavirus, naddala ku ngeri enkola y'okwetegereza eyakolebwa okuziyiza ekirwadde kya coronavirus gy'ejja okuggibwawo ng'akabi kaguddewo.
Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisukka mu 100 byafulumya sitatimenti nga biyita okukugira okulondoola ng'okwo.
Entegeka zino era zaalangirira ebintu munaana ebyetaagisa ku mirimu gya gavumenti:
Okuziyiza kulina kuba "kwa mateeka, kwa bwetaavu era kwa bwenkanya";
Okugattako, okulondoola n'okwetegereza birina okubaako n'ebiragiro ebikwata ku kiseera eky'okukomya;
Okukozesa obubaka kulina kuba kwa COVID-19 kwokka;
Obukuumi bw'ebikukwatako n'obutebenkevu bw'obwannanyini byo birina okukuumibwa era n'okwolesebwa nga byesigamiziddwa ku bujulizi.
Okulabirira kwa digito kulina okwewala okusosola n'okusuulibwa ku luuyi;
Okugabana kwonna kw'ebikwata ku bantu abalala ku mateeka kulina okussibwako essira;
Ebintu eby'okukuuma obutakozesa bubi bintu ebirina okuteekebwawo era n'eddembe ly'abantu okukuuma eddembe lyabwe erikwata ku kukozesa obubi lirina okukuumibwa;
"Okuyingizaamu amaanyi" okuva mu "b'omugaso bonna abakwatibwako", omuli abakugu mu by'obulamu n'ebibinja ebiruddewo ku mulamwa, kyetaagisa. Chaos Computer Club (CCC) ey'omu Bugirimaani ne Reporter ohne Grenzen (RSF) nabyo byafulumizza olukalala lw'okunoonyereza.
Enteekateeka ya Google/Apple etegekeddwa okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okwetegereza okw'emirembe gyonna nga baggyamu ebyuma ebikolera ku masimu amangu ddala nga tebikyetaagisa.
Amawanga agamu galiko eby'okukola nga bakozesa web based tracking mu kifo ky'okukozesa apps, nga kino kiviirako abantu obutasobola kuzannyira ku app era ne basobola n'okwewala okuzuula.
Mu Isiraeri, abakungu baatandika okukozesa enkola ey'okunoonya abantu nga bakozesa emikutu.
Naye eby'okuddamu ebyesigamiziddwa ku mikutu gya Internet ebiyinza okufuna obubaka obusooka ku bifo birina ebizibu bingi eby'obuntu.
Kyokka, si buli nkola erina omusenero omukulu eyetaaga okufuna obubaka bw'ekifo ky'omuntu; enkola ezimu ez'okukuuma obukuumi ezikozesa omusenero omukulu okuwuliziganya bokka (laba akatundu akaddako wansi).
Mu South Korea, abakungu baakozesa enkola ey'obutaba na programu okusobola okunoonyereza ku bantu.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa programu eya kalonda, enkola ekozesa obubaka obuggibwa mu nsi ezitali zimu, omuli obubaka obuggibwa ku byuma ebikwatagana n'okukozesa kaadi, era n'ebikwatako n'ebikwata ku bantu abalina obulwadde.
Ng'oggyeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abo abayinza okubaako kye bakolawo, gavumenti era ekoze obubaka bw'ebifo okuweebwa abantu bonna, nga kino kisobozeddwa olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu mateeka ag'obwannannyini oluvannyuma lw'ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekivaako obulwadde bwa Middle East Respiratory Syndrome.
Amagezi gano gali ku mikutu gya Internet n'ebirala bingi. Amawanga, nga Germany, gatandise okulowooza ku kukozesa enkola ez'obukuumi n'ez'obukuumi.
Nga 6 omwezi gwa April, 2020, ebintu ebirala ku nsonga eno tebinnayogerwa.
Okukwata abantu ab'enjawulo nga bakuuma obukuumi kye kigendererwa ekikolera era ekiragiddwa obulungi era nga kiwagirwa ebitabo eby'amaanyi okuva mu 2013. Nga April 7, 2020, ebibinja by'abakugu ebisukka mu kkumi byakola ku ngeri y'okutuukiriza obukuumi, gamba nga Bluetooth (BLE) ey'amaanyi amatono okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ku ssimu endala.
Kyokka, BBB-PT yali kufuba kwa kukwatagana okuli enkola zonna ez'obukiiko n'obutongole, so si nkola emu. Enkola ez'obukiiko ezirimu ezirimu eby'obukuumi (DPBT/DP-3T), nnamba z'okuyimba ez'ekiseera (TCN, ezaali zimanyiddwa nga nnamba z'okutuukirira, CNE), enkola ezikwata ku bulambulukufu, enkola z'okuzuula abalwadde (PACT) n'endala.
Mu nkola zino, obubaka obwawula omuntu ku munne tebuva ku kyuma, era byonna ebifaanagana bibaawo ku kyuma.
Ekibinja ky'obwannannyini ku MIT Media Lab kyali kikulaakulanya SafePaths, ekitebe eky'okukozesa tekinologiya ow'obwannannyini ng'okozesa ebiwandiiko by'ekifo oba eby'okuyitamu era n'okukozesa okusobola okunoonyereza ku kubuna kwa COVID-19.
Kino kyesigamiziddwa ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa okuva mu alipoota eyitibwa "The Bad Face of Apps: Maintaining Personal Privacy Under the Pandemic" eyafulumizibwa mu March 2020. Enigma MPC's SafeTrace Platform, kkampuni ekola ku by'obuntu eyava mu MIT Media Lab, y'emu ku nteekateeka zino.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya wa hardware omutebenkevu okuleka abakozesa okugabana obubaka bw'ekifo n'obw'obulamu n'abakozesa abalala n'abafuzi nga tebukosa bwekubiira.
Nga 5 omwezi gwa April, 2020, ekibiina kya Global Contact Tracker Alliance kyatandikibwawo ebibiina ebirina omwagaanya ku ngeri gye byali bikwataganamu n'enteekateeka ez'enjawulo, nga kigendererwa kya kugabanya busente era n'okuyamba abantu okussaamu amaanyi mu nkola ez'okuzuula n'okutegeeza, ekintu ekikulu ekinaasobozesa enkola ezo okukozesebwa ennyo.
Nga 9 April 2020, gavumenti ya Singapore yalangirira nti yali efulumizza enkola ya Blue Trace, ekozesebwa gavumenti.
Nga 10 omwezi gwa April, 2020, Google ne Apple, amakampuni agafuga ebyuma ebikozesebwa ku Android ne iOS, gaalangirira enteekateeka y'okunoonyereza ku bantu; nga bagamba nti bajja kukuuma obukuumi nga beesigama ku kukozesa tekinologiya wa Bluetooth omutono n'okukweka obubaka.
Era baafulumya n'obutegeeza ku tekinologiya omukulu ogukozesebwa mu nkola.
Okusinziira ku Apple ne Google, ekigendererwa kwe kuteekawo enkola mu mitendera esatu, nga:
Okuteekawo ebyuma ebikakasa gavumenti okuzimba enkola ez'obwannannyini ez'omu mateeka ez'okunoonyereza ku coronavirus.
Okugatta obulungi buno butereevu mu Android ne iOS nga Google ne Apple bateekateeka okugonjoola ebizibu by'okukozesa n'okwetegereza nga basooka kugabira enkola nga bayita mu kuggyawo enkola y'okuteekawo n'oluvannyuma nga bagiggyawo mu ngeri y'emu ng'obutabanguko bumaze.
Okudda mu nkola (ekirala ekimanyiddwa nga okudda mu nkola, okudda mu nkola, okukyusa ekigendererwa oba okukyusa eddagala) kwe kuddamu okukozesa eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba obulwadde oba embeera ey'ekisawo ey'enjawulo ku eyo gye lyali litegekeddwa okujjanjaba.
Eno y'emu ku ngeri z'okunoonyereza abakugu kwe bakola mu kiseera kino okuzuula obujjanjabi obumatiza n'obwangu mu COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza okulala kuzingiramu okukulaakulanya eddagala lya COVID-19 n'okuleeta plasma. SARS-CoV-2 erina obusawo 66 obujjanjabibwa eddagala, era buli emu erina ebifo bingi eby'okuteekawo obubonero.
Okunoonyereza ku bifo bino ebifaanagana kiwa pulaani ekakasa ku kukuza eddagala erikola ku bulwadde obw'omusaayi erizikiriza obutoffaali bwa COVID-19.
Mu bupolyteni bwa SARS-CoV-2 obuli ku mulamwa omukulu kuliko protease, RNA polymerase, helixase, protein S, ne adenosine diphosphate ribophosphate.
Hussein A. A., n'abalala beekenneenya eddagala erimu eryali lirina okuteekebwamu enkola ey'okufaanana n'eddagala eryali lirina enkola ey'okufaanana n'eyo ey'okunoonyereza ku ngeri eddagala eryo gye liyinza okukolamu.
Chloroquine ddagala erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri abasawo lye bakozesa okujjanjaba endwadde ezimu ez'obutabaako nsa.
Nga 18 March, WHO yalangirira nti Chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine eyagikuumibwa nayo zisobola okubeera ku ddagala erina okunoonyerezaako ng'ekitundu ky'okugezesebwa kw'obulwadde.
Gavana wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okugezesebwa kwa New York State ku chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine kuyinza okutandika nga March 24. Nga March 28, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulphate ne chloroquine phosphate wansi w'ekigendererwa kya Emergency Use Authorization (EUA).
Okujjanjaba kuno tekukakasibwa mu nkola y'okugezesebwa kwa FDA era kukkiriziddwa mu ndagaano ya FDA ey'okukozesa mu mbeera ez'amangu kyokka ng'eddagala ery'okugezesa ery'okukozesa mu mbeera ez'amangu eri abalwadde abajjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro naye nga tebasobola kufuna bujjanjabi mu kugezesebwa.
CDC yategeeza nti "tekinnategeerekeka nti hydroxychloroquine ekozesebwa mu kuziyiza, okujjanjaba, eddagala oba ekiseera kya SARS-CoV-2".
Abasawo bagamba nti bakozesa eddagala nga "tebalina kya kukola".
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza abaava mu Turkey mu Istanbul kati bakola okunoonyereza ku ngeri y'okukozesaamu chlorine ng'oggyeko obuwuka bwa zinc, vitamin A, vitamin C, ne vitamin D.
Okunoonyereza okungi kukolebwa mu yunivasite ya Duke ne Oxford.
Yunivasite ya New York's Langone Medical School ekola okunoonyereza ku bukuumi n'obwanguzi bw'okukozesa hydroxychloroquine.
Okugezesebwa kw'ekinnansi mu China mu Wuhan ne Shenzhen kwagamba nti faviprovir yali "nnyangu nnyo".
Mu balwadde 35 mu Shenzhen, ebyava mu kukebera byali bibi okumala ennaku nga 4, ate abalwadde 45 abataafuna bulwadde obwo baamala ennaku 11.
Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu Wuhan ku balwadde 240 abalina omusujja gw'amawuggwe, kimu kya kubiri kyaweebwa favifir ne kimu kya kubiri kyaweebwa omyenofir.
Ekitongole ky'eddagala ekya Italy kyalabula abantu nti obujulizi obuliwo obuwagira eddagala lino tebumala era nga bukyali bwa kusooka.
Nga Apuli 2, Bugirimaani yalangirira nti ejja kugula eddagala okuva mu Japan okuligatta ku bugagga bwayo, era eggye lirina kukozesa eddagala lino okutwala mu malwaliro ga yunivasite, gye lirina okukozesebwa okujjanjaba abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Okusinziira ku South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe ayogedde ne gavumenti ya Trump ku kugula eddagala lino. Eddagala lino liyinza okuba nga terina mugaso gwonna mu kujjanjaba abalwadde abakulu ennyo nga n'akawuka ka Corona kaali kaakula.
Kiyinza obutaba kya bukuumi eri abakazi ab'embuto oba ab'ekiruubirirwa eky'okufuna olubuto.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa nga bakozesa lupinavir/retonavir (Calitra), eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka ka lupinavir ne retonavir, kwalaga nti ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza "tebyalina mugaso".
Eddagala lino lyali lya kukola ku HIV okugiziyiza okuzaala nga ligatta ku protease.
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza ku yunivasite ya Colorado bagezaako okukyusa eddagala okuzuula ekika ekikwatagana ne SARS-CoV-2 protease. Ekibiina ky'obusawo kivumiriddwa olw'okuzza ensimbi mu ddagala erikola ku HIV/AIDS.
Ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu kyongeddewo lupinavir/ritonavir mu kugezesebwa kw'ensi yonna.
Gilead Sciences yatandikawo eddagala eriyitibwa Remdesivir ng'eddagala erirwanyisa obulwadde bwa Ebola ne Marburg. Gilead Sciences yakizuula nti Remdesivir erina ebirwadde ebirwanyisa akawuka ka siriimu, akawuka ka mukka, ne korona.
Ekimu ku bizibu ebiva mu bujjanjabi bwa anti-virus kwe kukulaakulanya obuvumu okuyita mu nkyukakyuka eziyinza okuvaamu endwadde ez'amaanyi n'okuzisaasaanya.
Ebigezo ebimu eby'olubereberye biraga nti Remdesivir esobola okuba n'omutindo omukulu ogw'obusobozi bw'okuziyiza. Waliwo ebigezo bingi ebikolebwa mu malwaliro, omuli bibiri ebikolebwa Cleveland University Hospitals; ekimu ku bantu abalina obulwadde obutonotono, ate ekirala ku balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Waliwo okunoonyereza kwa mirundi esatu ku vitamin C ku balwadde abajjanjabirwa mu ddwaliro nga balwadde nnyo olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19, era n'okunoonyereza kwa mirundi ebiri okufuuliddwa okufuga (China, Canada) n'okunoonyereza okutali kufuga (Italy).
Ekitundu kya New York kyatandika okugezesa ebikolwa bya azithromycin nga March 24, 2020.
