Ebiwandiiko bino tebirina kiseera, era bigoberera abantu okuva ku mulwadde okutuuka ku mbeera gy'alimu.
Wadde ng'emirambo egirwanyisa obulwadde tegisobola kufulumira mu bantu bonna abalina obulwadde, okubeerawo kwagyo kuyinza okuwa obubaka ku muwendo gw'abantu abalina obulwadde.
Mu kibuga ky'e Italy, Castelloni d'Adda, ekibuga ekimu ekirina abantu 4,600, abantu 80 (1,7%) be baafa.
Mu Janglet, obulwadde bwabuna olw'embaga z'omukolo, ne busengukira mu bavubuka, ne kiviirako abantu okufa obutono, era oboolyawo abantu bonna abafa COVID-19 tebaatwalibwa ng'abafa olw'obulwadde obwo.
Ate era, obujjanjabi mu Bugirimaani tebukendedde.
Mu Netherlands, abantu nga 3 ku buli kikumi bayinza okuba nga balina ebitundu by'omubiri ebirwanyisa obulwadde, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bantu abawaddeyo omusaayi.
Abantu 69 (0.004% ku bantu) bakakasibwa okufa COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino n'omuwendo gw'abafa gwa njawulo wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi.
Abasajja be basinga okufa mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu China ne Italy.
Abasajja baba mu kabi akasingawo nga bali mu myaka 50, ate ng'enjawulo wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi eziriko zibula ku myaka 90.
Mu China, okufa kwa buli musajja kwali 2.8 ku buli kikumi ate okw'omukazi kwali 1.7 ku buli kikumi.
Ensonga eziviirako enjawulo zino ez'ekikula tezimanyiddwa, naye obuzaale n'enneeyisa biyinza okuba nga bye bireetawo.
Obutafaanagana mu by'omubiri okusinziira ku kikula, obutafaanana kwa bakazi okunywa ssigala, n'abasajja okufuna endwadde ez'omugaso gamba ng'omusaayi ogusukkiridde nga bakyali bato okusinga abakazi, biyinza okuba nga byaviirako abasajja okufa.
Mu Bulaaya, 57% ku abo abafunye obulwadde bwa COVID-19 baali basajja ate 72% ku abo abafudde baali basajja.
Okutuusa mu Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Amerika tegikyagoberera bubaka bwa buliri obukwata ku bulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti endwadde ez'obulabe nga Ebola, HIV, ekikulukuto, ne SARS zikwata ku basajja n'abakazi mu ngeri ya njawulo.
Abakozi b'ebyobulamu, naddala bannamukadde, basajja nnyo era balina obunafu bw'okusannyalala akawuka.
Ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu kyalangirira nga 11 Febwali 2020 nti erinnya ly'ekirwadde erya bulijjo lya "COVID-19".
Akulira ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yategeezezza nti, Ko kye kivvuunula ekigambo Corona, ate nga mu kivvuunula kya Virus, Wd kye kivvuunula obulwadde era 19 kitegeeza omwaka ekirwadde kino we kyasookera okuzuulibwa: 31 December 2019.
Erinnya lyalondebwa okwewala okwogerako ku kifo ekimu (ng'ekika kya China), ekika ky'ensolo oba abantu, okusinziira ku magezi g'ensi yonna ag'okuyita abantu nga gaagala okwewala okuvumibwa. Akawuka akaviirako COVID-19 kayitibwa coronavirus 2 ekwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS-CoV-2).
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, WHO ekozesa ebigambo "akawuka ka COVID-19" ne "akawuka akaviirako COVID-19" mu bubaka obutegeerekeka obulungi.
Obulwadde n'akawuka bitera okuyitibwa "kovirosi ya Corona".
Mu kiseera eky'obulwadde obwasooka mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byayitibwa "Koronavirus" ne "Wuhan Corona Virus".
Mu January 2020, Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'ensi yonna (WHO) kyawa amagezi okukozesa amannya gano: Novel Coronavirus-2019 ne Novel Coronavirus-related acute respiratory illness-2019 nga amannya ag'akaseera ag'akawuka n'obulwadde okusinziira ku bulagirizi bwa 2015 obukugira okukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'endwadde n'akawuka.
Amannya abiri aga gavumenti COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gafulumizibwa nga 11 February 2020.
Olw'obusobozi obutonotono mu nkola y'okugaba, amakampuni ag'omulembe gafulumya ebintu eby'obujjanjabi gamba ng'ebimansulo n'ebitundu by'ebyuma eby'okuwummulamu.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, eddwaliro ly'omu Italy bwe lyali lyetaaga nnyo ekikopo ky'eby'okusiiga, era ng'abasuubuzi baali tebasobola kukiwa mu kiseera, kkampuni emu ey'omu kitundu yakyusa enkola n'ewaayo ekikopo 100 mu kiro kimu.
Oluvannyuma lw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwasooka, endowooza z'obukumpanya, obubaka obutali butuufu n'obukuusa obukwata ku nsibuko y'obulwadde, omuwendo gwabwo, okutangira, okubujjanjaba n'ebirala byajjawo era ne bisaasaana mangu ku Internet.
Kirabika abantu basobola okuleeta akawuka ku nsolo endala.
Okunoonyereza kwalemererwa okuzuula obujulizi obulaga nti akawuka kano kaali mu mbizzi, ebinazi, n'enkoko.
Tewali ddagala oba bulwadde bwonna obuvumirirwa okujjanjaba obulwadde buno.
Ebitongole bya gavumenti, ebibiina by'obuyigirize n'abanoonyereza mu makolero bakola okunoonyereza okw'ensi yonna ku ddagala n'obuyambi bwa COVID-19.
Mu March, WHO yatandikawo "okugezesebwa kw'obumu" okukebera ebikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bw'ebika bya anti-virus ebina ebikyasinze okuba ebyesigika.
Tewali ddagala lirina kukozesebwa, naye ebitongole eby'enjawulo bikolera ku ddagala erigenda okuteekebwamu.
Bakolera ku by'okuyiga ebyasooka ku SARS-CoV kubanga efaanana ne SARS-CoV-2 mu kukozesa ACE2 okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu.
Enkola ssatu ez'okuzaala zikebeddwa.
Okusooka, abanoonyereza baagala okuteekawo eddagala erigema akawuka.
Okukozesa akawuka kano, ka kube nga tekakyaliwo oba nga kafiiridde, kigendererwa kya kuleetawo obuyambi bw'omubiri mu bwangu okuziyiza obulwadde obuggya bwa COVID-19.
Enkola ey'okubiri, eddagala erikola ku bitundu by'omusaayi, erina ekigendererwa eky'okuteekawo eddagala erikola ku mubiri okuziyiza obuwuka obw'obulabe.
Mu mbeera ya SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza kuno kwesigamye ku protein eya SpikeS eyamba akawuka okuyingira mu biwundu bya ACE2.
Enkola eyokusatu y'okulwanyisa ekirwadde kya DNA (ekirwadde kya DNA ekirimu langi oba ekirwadde kya RNA, enkola empya ey'okuvvuunula ekirwadde).
Okugezaako okulwanyisa obulwadde obuva mu nkola zino byonna kulina okugezesebwa okusobola okukakasa nti si mbi era nti bikola bulungi. Nga 16, Maaki 2020, okugezesebwa okwasooka okw'ekirwadde kino kwatandika ku bannakyewa bana mu Seattle.
Ekirwadde kino kirimu code y'ekika ekitali kya kabi ekikoppololwa okuva ku kawuka ako. Okuteekawo obuwuka obuteesigama ku bulwadde buno kye kizibu ekirala ekirina okukolebwa mu kutonda eddagala lya SARS-CoV-2, naye kino kyawukanako.
Waliwo okugezesebwa kwa ddwaaliro okusukka mu 300 okwaliwo okuva mu Apuli 2020.
Okugezesebwa musanvu kujjanjabibwa dda endwadde ya siriimu, nga kuno kwalimu okunoonyereza kwa hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Eddagala eriragiddwa ery'okulwanyisa akawuka ka siriimu eririna okukozesebwa mu kujjanjaba obulwadde obupya lye lisinga okunoonyereza mu China, nga lirina ebigezo bya Remdesivir ebiwumbi mwenda mu mawanga agatali gamu era ebinaavaamu bijja kuteebwa ku nkomerero ya Apuli.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi okwakolebwa ku nkulaakulana y'ekikopo n'eddagala erisobola okujjanjaba COVID-19 kwatandika mu April 2020. Eddagala erimu eriyitibwa remdesivir, chloroquine, hydroxychloroquine, lupinavir/ritonavir, lupinavir/itonavir erikwataganyizibwa ne interferon beta, lirina okugezesebwa.
Waliwo obujulizi obusooka ku buwanguzi bwa Remdesivir, okuva mu Maaki 2020.
Obulwadde bw'omusaayi bweyongedde okulongooka mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa eddagala lya Remdesivir ery'okuteeka mu lubuto.
Okugezesebwa kw'ekibinja eky'okusatu mu Amerika, China ne Italy. Chloroquine, eyakozesebwanga eddagala lya malaria, yasomebwa mu China mu Febwali 2020 era erina ebivudde mu kusooka.
Kyokka, waliwo ebibuuzo ebibuuzibwa ku kunoonyereza.
Ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu Korea ne China bakubiriza okukozesa kloroquine.
Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Virology Research Institute kigamba nti wadde nga kiragira eddagala erimu, okulisazaamu kya kabi nnyo era kiyinza okuviirako omuntu okufa.
Nga 28 March 2020, FDA yafulumya olukusa olw'okukozesa mu bwangu hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine okusinziira ku magezi g'abasawo abajjanjaba abantu abalina COVID-19. Enkola ya China eya 7 era erimu ne interferon, ribevirin oba omyfenovir ey'okukozesa okujjanjaba COVID-19.
Ebyafaayo biraga nti eddagala eriyitibwa ribavirin eringi lyetaagisa okulemesa SARS-CoV-2 mu laboratory.
Okunoonyereza okungi ku bikolwa bya nitasoxanide ku bitonde by'ensi kunakulirwa oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti eremesa ensangi ez'obutiti bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okunoonyereza ku chlorokine ne hydroxychloroquine nga n'azithromycin oba nedda, kuzzeemu obuzibu obw'amaanyi obwaleetera abasawo obutakkiriza bujjanjabi buno nga tebannayongera kunoonyereza. Oseltamivir terimenya SARS-CoV-2 mu laboratory era terina mulimu gwonna gw'ekola mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Omukka gwa cytokine guyinza okuba omu ku bizibu ebiva mu COVID-19 ey'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine esobola okuba n'ebika eby'okulwanyisa omuyaga gwa cytokine. Ekitongole kya China eky'ebyobulamu kyongedde tossilizumab mu bulagirizi bw'obujjanjabi oluvannyuma lw'okumaliriza okunoonyereza okutono.
