Ng'oggyeko okukozesebwa mu kukebera serum ya viratin okunoonyereza ku bubenje bwa cytokine, era kigendereddwaako okuziyiza ebikolwa ng'ebyo, ekisuubirwa okutta abantu abamu.
FDA yakkiriza eddagala eriyitibwa Interleukin-6 receptor receptor, ery'okussaako obutoffaali bwa T-cell obuggya ku antibodi ya khmer, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku mbeera y'okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa Steroid-nonresponsive cytokine-secretion syndrome mu 2017.
N'okutuusa kati, tewali bukakafu bulaga nti tossilizumab ddagala ddungi eri obulwadde bwa cytokine.
Engeri y'okusindika obuwuka obuziyiza obulwadde obuggiddwawo n'obuteekeddwateekeddwako obuva mu byuma by'omubiri eby'abalwadde abawonye COVID-19 eri abo ababyetaaga, eyigirizibwa ng'engeri y'okuteeka eddagala ku bantu.
Enkola eno yagezesebwa ku SARS era ebyavaamu tebyali birungi.
Okuggyawo akawuka kano kye kintu ekisuubirwa ekiruma eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka kano okufuuka ekirwanyisa ku SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, waliwo enkola endala eziyinza okukozesebwa, gamba ng'obutwa obuva ku bulwadde obuyitibwa antibody-based cellular toxicity oba obutwa obuva ku kulya omwenge oba byombi.
Waliwo engeri endala ez'okujjanjaba n'omubiri ogutafa, gamba ng'okukozesa omubiri ogutafa, ogukozesebwa mu kulwanyisa endwadde.
Omusaayi gw'omulwadde oguva mu bulwadde buno guyinza okufulumizibwa ne gukulaakulana.
